A major exhibition of Modern and Contemporary sculpture entitled will be held at Chatsworth in Derbyshire this fall. Works by artists such as Jean Dubuffet, Antony Gormley, Aristide Maillol and James Turrell will be exhibited and all will be
Beyond Limits
 
