On March 21, during Asia Week in New York, Sotheby's Chinese Contemporary Art department will hold its spring sale of Contemporary Asian Art, estimated to bring $18/26 million**. Works by Zhang Xiaogang, Yue Minjun, Xu Bing Ai Weiwei, and a significant group of Chinese artists practicing in the school of Neorealism will be featured. The highlight of the sale is Zhang Xiaogang's
st
