On April 16 and 17 in New York, Sotheby's will be holding its third annual combined Russian Paintings and Works of Art sale, featuring works by Ivan Aivazovsky, Dmitrievich Grigoriev and Mikhail Nesterov, among others. The sale will also feature a section devoted to Russian Contemporary Art. The total sale is expected to realize $40 million**.
