which sold for $4.5 million, above the pre-sale estimate of $2/3 million
3
.
In our June Antiquities sale in New York, the auction record for any sculpture was shattered when the beautiful bronze statue
Artemis and the Stag
sold for an outstanding $28.6 million, more than four times the pre-sale high estimate of $7 million
