Employee Loans and Affiliate Transactions
                    (a) Except as disclosed in , no Sotheby Entity shall enter into or be a party to any transaction with any other Sotheby Entity or any Affiliate thereof except in the ordinary course of and pursuant to the reasonable requirements of such Sotheby Entity's business and, in the case of any transaction with any Affiliate thereof (other than another Sotheby Entity), upon fair and reasonable terms that are no less favorable to such Sotheby Entity than would be obtained in a comparable arm's length transaction with a Person not an Affiliate of such Sotheby Entity.
