In London next week, Sotheby's will present the collection of the renowned actor, director and film producer Lord Richard Attenborough and his wife, Lady Attenborough. The sale is made up of a fine selection of works from some of the leading British artists of the 20 Century and is expected to bring in excess of $3.2 million. The highlight of the sale is by LS Lowry which is estimated at $500,000-$840,000.
