The Culbertson Guidon
And on December 17, Sotheby's final auction of the year will be the sale in New York of the celebrated collection of toy boats, soldiers, motorcycles and classic board games lovingly gathered over nearly four decades by legendary collector Malcolm Forbes and his sons. Each area of the collection is among the finest of its kind, including rare and important examples by the leading toy makers in the field  from a Mrklin recreation of the Cunard Line's
