e Fronting Lender. At any time any Lender is a Non-Funding Lender, at Agent's election at any time or upon any L/C Issuer's, the Swing Line Lender's or the Fronting Lender's written request delivered to Agent (whether before or after the occurrence of any Default or Event of Default), participating interests in any newly made Swing Line Loan or Sterling Revolving Credit Advance or any newly issued or modified Letter of Credit will be allocated among non-Defaulting Lenders in a manner consistent with this Section 9.9(d)(ii).
                                         
