Exhibit 99.1
The Magnificent Jewels sale in New York in April was Sotheby's best ever, and brought $43.2 million, significantly above the pre-sale high estimate of $31.1 million. The auction saw notable prices for beautiful estate jewels, white and colored diamonds, precious gems and natural pearls, with seven pieces bringing more than $1 million
