 means the property covered by the Domestic Collateral Documents and the Foreign Collateral Documents and any other property, real or personal, tangible or intangible, now existing or hereafter acquired, that may at any time be or become subject to a security interest or Lien in favor of Agent, on the Secured Parties, to secure the Secured Obligations.
