plus
(ii) the aggregate amount of cash of the Sotheby Entities (as determined in accordance with GAAP) at such time
minus
(c) the amount of such cash subject to a Lien (or held in a deposit or securities account subject to a Lien) in favor of any Person other than (i) Agent or a (ii) consignor to whom such cash is due to be paid in respect of the sale of a Work of Art consigned by such Person to the Sotheby Entities for sale
minus
(d) without duplication of the foregoing
clause (c)
, the amount of such cash subject to any restriction on withdrawal from the deposit or securities account in which such cash is held.
