 means, with respect to any amount denominated in Hong Kong Dollars, such amount of Hong Kong Dollars, and with respect to any amount denominated in a currency other than Hong Kong Dollars, the amount of Hong Kong Dollars, as of any date of determination, into which such other currency (as the context may require) can be converted in accordance with
